34:52.159 --> 34:55.794
♪♪

35:04.838 --> 35:06.572
Billis:
Wake up, buttercup.

35:08.108 --> 35:09.841
I'm gonna go
take a piss.

35:09.843 --> 35:12.310
My partner's gonna
ask you some questions.

35:12.312 --> 35:16.048
♪♪

35:19.519 --> 35:22.921
We've got
a lot to talk about.

35:22.923 --> 35:24.023
[ Screams ]

35:24.792 --> 35:26.692
Ohh!
Time to get up.

35:30.130 --> 35:32.598
Where's the dog?

35:32.600 --> 35:34.600
What dog?

35:34.602 --> 35:37.936
The dog
that shit in my mouth.

35:37.938 --> 35:40.472
I'm gonna
make you some coffee.

35:40.474 --> 35:41.607
Yes.

35:41.609 --> 35:43.075
Excuse me.

35:43.077 --> 35:46.045
♪♪

35:50.818 --> 35:52.818
[ Jay vomiting ]

35:52.820 --> 35:55.054
♪♪

36:00.494 --> 36:03.595
[ Groaning ]

36:07.234 --> 36:10.436
You saved my life.

36:10.438 --> 36:13.505
Thank you.

36:13.507 --> 36:16.108
Uh-huh.
[ Toilet flushes ]

36:18.178 --> 36:20.712
There's an address.

36:20.714 --> 36:23.915
Do you know who he is?

36:23.917 --> 36:26.784
Who?

36:26.786 --> 36:29.121
Ivanovich Victor Sepp.

36:29.123 --> 36:33.158
♪♪

36:39.066 --> 36:40.132
I know him now.

36:42.536 --> 36:46.071
Well, I-I don't know him,
but I've been seeing him.

36:46.073 --> 36:49.607
He's been following me
around a long time -- years.

36:49.609 --> 36:51.009
Years?

36:51.011 --> 36:52.711
Yeah.

36:55.883 --> 36:58.283
[ Snorting ]

36:58.285 --> 37:00.085
You looking
for Tamar, too?

37:03.157 --> 37:04.490
Yeah.

37:04.492 --> 37:07.893
You know
where she is?

37:07.895 --> 37:09.495
Maybe.

37:09.497 --> 37:11.864
[ Kettle whistling ]
Maybe.

37:14.368 --> 37:17.035
I'll make you a deal.

37:17.037 --> 37:19.437
Find out
why that guy was...

37:19.439 --> 37:21.974
And then you and I will go
together and talk to Tamar.

37:24.444 --> 37:26.778
Yeah. Okay, sure.
I can do that.

37:26.780 --> 37:30.182
I can, uh, check his place out,
see what I can see.

37:30.184 --> 37:32.184
I'll go today.

37:32.186 --> 37:34.252
Why do you want to know?

37:34.254 --> 37:36.522
Why are<i>you</i>looking
for Tamar so bad?

37:38.992 --> 37:40.859
Tamar's not the, uh --
not the story.

37:40.861 --> 37:45.331
It's George Hodel.

37:45.333 --> 37:47.733
She...

37:47.735 --> 37:50.869
She knows something
or knew something.

37:54.141 --> 37:55.607
What thing?

37:55.609 --> 37:59.477
Uh, George Hodel was involved
in criminal activity,

37:59.479 --> 38:01.279
and one of the thing--
one of the many things

38:01.281 --> 38:03.749
he was doing
was running an abortion clinic

38:03.751 --> 38:07.252
out of Hollywood,
which is illegal.

38:09.557 --> 38:12.090
Abortion?
That's what this is about?

38:12.092 --> 38:13.359
Well, it's about
other things, too,

38:13.361 --> 38:16.094
but nothing I'm sure of.

38:16.096 --> 38:17.695
Look, I'm not gonna
help you write a story

38:17.697 --> 38:20.766
that hurts my mother
and my family.

38:20.768 --> 38:23.435
So, leave her out.
And me.

38:23.437 --> 38:27.906
No, don't write about me.
Don't ask about me, okay?

38:27.908 --> 38:30.108
Yeah, I got it.

38:30.110 --> 38:32.244
I just want the truth.
That's all.

38:32.246 --> 38:34.613
♪♪

38:37.585 --> 38:39.818
♪♪

38:42.923 --> 38:45.724
I think maybe Tamar
is in Hawaii.

38:48.596 --> 38:49.995
You get me a plane ticket
to Hawaii,

38:49.997 --> 38:53.131
and we'll go
talk to her together.

38:53.133 --> 38:56.802
I'll get you the complete
address when we get there.

38:56.804 --> 38:58.604
Just promise me
you'll take me with you.

38:58.606 --> 39:02.340
Hawaii, huh?

39:02.342 --> 39:04.009
Shake my hand?

39:04.011 --> 39:07.446
♪♪

39:16.957 --> 39:18.957
♪♪

39:24.031 --> 39:26.432
♪♪

39:34.041 --> 39:36.709
♪♪

39:44.051 --> 39:46.352
♪♪

